-- Gome Approves Founder Huang's Representatives to Board, Cable TV Reports
-- B y   W e n d y   L e u n g
-- 2010-12-17T04:56:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-17/gome-approves-founder-huang-s-representatives-to-board-cable-tv-reports.html
Gome Electrical Appliances Holdings
Ltd., China’s second-biggest electronics retailer, approved the
appointment of founder Huang Guangyu’s representatives to the
company’s board, Cable TV reported today.  Gome approved Zou Xiao Chun and Huang Yan Hong to join the
board as directors, the Hong Kong-based broadcaster said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wendy Leung in Hong Kong at 
 wleung12@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
